.\" Manpage for Process Manager
.TH PROCESS_MANAGER 1 "May 2024" "1.0" "Process Manager "

.SH NAME
Process Manager \- interactive process management utility

.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBProcess Manager\fR 

.SH DESCRIPTION
The \fBprocess_manager\fR utility provides a simple interactive interface to manage processes on the system. It allows users to list all processes, list processes grouped by user, display process IDs, run/stop specific processes, and send specific signals to processes.

.SH OPTIONS
There are no command-line options for \fBprocess_manager\fR. Upon execution, it presents an interactive menu.

.SH INTERACTIVE MENU
\fBprocess_manager\fR provides an interactive menu for users to choose options from. The menu prompts the user to enter a number corresponding to the desired action.

.SH MENU OPTIONS
.TP
\fB1.\fR List all processes in the system.
.TP
\fB2.\fR List all processes grouped by user.
.TP
\fB3.\fR Display process ID of all processes.
.TP
\fB4.\fR Run/stop a specific process.
.TP
\fB5.\fR Send specific signals to specific process.
.TP
\fB6.\fR Exit the process manager.

.SH AUTHOR
Mazen Mohamed
